OL,6,FLegislation to ensure people are never
OL,7,Frestricted from visiting dying loved
OL,8,Fones is needed, campaigners have said
OL,9,Fahead of the first UK Covid-19 Inquiry
OL,10,Fsitting in Belfast.
OL,12,FThe UK-wide inquiry's hearings in
OL,13,FBelfast begin on Tuesday and will run
OL,14,Ffor three weeks and are designed to
OL,15,Fprovide an opportunity to look in
OL,16,F"depth" at the decisions taken in
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland.
