OL,3,CUK-wide Covid-19 inquiry to begin
OL,4,Csittings in Belfast
OL,6,FA campaign group representing bereaved
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland families will hold a
OL,8,Fpublic gathering to coincide with the
OL,9,Ffirst day of the Belfast sittings.
OL,11,FThose who lost loved ones to the virus
OL,12,Fare being invited to attend the event
OL,13,Fat 9.15am outside the Clayton Hotel,
OL,14,Fdressed in red while holding
OL,15,Fphotographs of those they lost during
OL,16,Fthe pandemic.
OL,18,FMarion Reynolds, a member of Northern
OL,19,FIreland Covid Bereaved Families for
OL,20,FJustice campaign group, will give
OL,21,Fevidence during Tuesday's hearing.
