OL,4,Csittings in Belfast
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of her inquiry
OL,7,Fappearance, she told how her aunt,
OL,8,FMarie Reynolds, contracted Covid
OL,9,Fduring a hospital admission before
OL,10,Fbeing discharged to a care home where
OL,11,Fshe subsequently died.
OL,13,FMs Reynolds said: "During my aunt's
OL,14,Ftime in hospital and the care home I
OL,15,Fwas unable to visit her, even though
OL,16,Fcare partner guidance had been issued
OL,17,Ffrom the Department of Health to
OL,18,Ffacilitate such visits for carers,"
OL,19,Fshe said.
