OL,4,Csittings in Belfast
OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Covid-19 Bereaved
OL,7,FFamilies for Justice campaign group is
OL,8,Fled by bereaved daughters Martina
OL,9,FFerguson and Brenda Doherty.
OL,11,FMs Ferguson, a Portadown woman whose
OL,12,Fmother, Ursula Derry, contracted the
OL,13,Fvirus and died in a care home in
OL,14,FJanuary 2021, said a thorough
OL,15,Finvestigation needs to take place.
