OL,3,CUK-wide Covid-19 inquiry to begin
OL,4,Csittings in Belfast
OL,6,FShe said: "We need to find out what
OL,7,Fwent wrong, what went right and what
OL,8,Fdecisions were made specifically for
OL,9,Fand in Northern Ireland, who made the
OL,10,Fdecisions and on what basis and
OL,11,Fscientific advice were they taken."
OL,13,FShe added: "We need changes in
OL,14,Flegislation that no-one will ever be
OL,15,Frestricted from their loved ones again
OL,16,For be allowed to die alone."
