OL,4,Csittings in Belfast
OL,6,FMs Doherty, from Newtownabbey, lost
OL,7,Fher mother Ruth Burke to hospital
OL,8,Facquired Covid-19. Mrs Burke was the
OL,9,Ffirst woman in Northern Ireland to
OL,10,Flose her life to the virus in March
OL,11,F2020.
OL,13,F"It's important for us to hear, who
OL,14,Fwas it that communicated advice and to
OL,15,Fwhom in the administration did they
OL,16,Fadvise, how did this inform the
OL,17,Fdecisions made," she said.
