OL,6,F"This is not the time for party
OL,7,Fpolitics or point scoring but to be
OL,8,Fopen and transparent in regard to the
OL,9,Foverall management of all aspects of
OL,10,Fthe pandemic."
OL,12,FOn a visit to Belfast, inquiry
OL,13,Fsecretary Ben Connah highlighted the
OL,14,Finquiry's Every Story Matters online
OL,15,Fplatform for people affected by the
OL,16,Fpandemic to share their stories.
OL,18,FHe encouraged people in Northern
OL,19,FIreland to use the site to detail
OL,20,Ftheir experiences.
