OL,4,Csittings in Belfast
OL,6,FThe inquiry has already held hearings
OL,7,Fin England, Scotland and Wales and Mr
OL,8,FConnah said it was crucial to examine
OL,9,Fthe situation across all the UK
OL,10,Fnations.
OL,12,FAsked if three weeks was sufficient to
OL,13,Fexamine the pandemic in Northern
OL,14,FIreland, he said: "Every single one of
OL,15,Fthe chair's investigations during the
OL,16,Flife of this inquiry is going to look
OL,17,Fat Northern Ireland, just as it will
OL,18,Flook at Scotland, Wales and England.
