OL,6,F"But we're here in Belfast for three
OL,7,Fvery intensive weeks of hearings,
OL,8,Fwhere we're really going to get into
OL,9,Fdepth about the core political
OL,10,Fdecisions that were taken from March
OL,11,F2020 through the pandemic, about the
OL,12,Frestrictions that applied to all the
OL,13,Fpeople that live in Northern Ireland,
OL,14,Fthe way that they were changed over
OL,15,Ftime, and the other really important
OL,16,Fdecisions that were taken there."
