OL,6,FAt a preliminary hearing in December,
OL,7,Fit emerged that WhatsApp messages sent
OL,8,Fby former Stormont ministers during
OL,9,Fthe pandemic have been lost after
OL,10,Fgovernment-issued electronic devices
OL,11,Fwere wiped.
OL,13,FThose included the devices of Lady
OL,14,FFoster and Ms O'Neill.
