OL,6,FAsked about the absence of those
OL,7,Fmessages, Mr Connah said: "We've heard
OL,8,Fa lot of evidence already in
OL,9,FEdinburgh, in Cardiff and in London,
OL,10,Fabout different aspects of the way
OL,11,Fdecisions were taken, including the
OL,12,Fuse of WhatsApp.
OL,14,F"So I'm pretty confident that the
OL,15,Fhearings over the next three weeks
OL,16,Fwill have access to a lot of the
OL,17,Fevidence that they need."
